description: City: Middletown, CT If you love desserts, you've heard of NoRA Cupcake Company, and if you haven't today is your lucky day!NoRa's Cupcake Company specializes in creating both aesthetically and orally pleasing bite sized desserts. A fan favorite and must-try is the Irish Car Bomb cupcake. With chocolate Guiness cake, Jameson chocolate ganache and Bailey's cream cheese frosting, you would be hard-pressed to pass it up. However, if that doesn't appeal to your taste-buds, rest assured they've got an extensive menu and there is something for every sweet-toothed food truck lover. In addition they also feature a savory line of cakes which includes a roasted garlic cake and a tomato basil cake.
name: NoRA Cupcake Company
